#  E-Commerce Website Proposal (Lenskart-like Platform)

##  Project Overview
This project presents a business proposal for developing a full-featured e-commerce platform similar to Lenskart, specifically designed for an eyewear business.

The platform will allow users to explore and purchase spectacles, glasses, and lenses through a modern and user-friendly interface.

---

##  Objective
- Build a scalable and user-friendly e-commerce platform
- Provide seamless online shopping experience
- Enable easy product browsing and secure checkout

---

##  Scope of Work

### User Features
- User Registration & Login (Email / Mobile OTP)
- Product Browsing (Specs, Glasses, Lenses)
- Advanced Search & Filters
- Product Detail Page
- Add to Cart / Wishlist
- Address Management with Pincode Detection
- Secure Checkout & Payment Integration
- Order Tracking
- User Profile & Order History

---

### Admin Panel
- Dashboard
- Product Management
- Category & Inventory Management
- Order Management
- User Management
- Analytics & Reports

---

## Core Functionalities
- Responsive UI
- Payment Gateway Integration
- API-based Backend
- Secure Authentication
- SEO-friendly Structure

---

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: React.js
- Backend: Node.js (Express.js)
- Database: MongoDB

